---
title: Beef Mince & Mushroom Pie with Baby Spinach & Mash Potato Topping
description: There’s no need to wait in line at the bakery to get your hands on a comforting pie when you can whip one up at home in no time. For the filling, bake a saucy beef mince with mushrooms and spinach then spread over a mash potato top. There you have it, one tasty pie straight from your own oven!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
